description: Variable def and use, model input
text: 
- Hello,
- model: watsonx/ibm/granite-34b-code-instruct
  def: name
  parameters:
    stop: ["!"]
    include_stop_sequence: false
- "\n"
- model: watsonx/ibm/granite-20b-multilingual
  input:
      - "Translate the word '${ name | trim }' to French\n"
